reviewText: Don't listen to the haters! At times you'll be laughing at...well everybody in the cast except the two teenagers at the heart of this film. Real chemistry between them! Especially the girl Zoe Dean. Wow, what an actress. You can't tell what she's really feeling, and then all of a sudden it will be viscerally clear! She's amazing! Some very novel tortures, and some REALLY LAME ONES!
